CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

June 15, 2011

[Cite as 06/15/2011 Case Announcements, 2011-Ohio-2877.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2011-0049. State v. Vickers.

Franklin App. No. 10AP-318, 2010-Ohio-6178. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss granted. Cause dismissed.
